iv class="flex justify-center items-center"><div class="relative w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto aspect-video overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-md"><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gray-300"></div><div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center"><img src="/imgs/feature-tabs/hairstyle_ai_easy_select.png" alt="hairstyle_ai_easy_select" class="h-full object-cover"/></div></div></div></div></div><div data-state="inactive" data-orientation="horizontal" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="radix-_R_jausnj9flb_-trigger-instant-try-on" hidden="" id="radix-_R_jausnj9flb_-content-instant-try-on" tabindex="0" data-slot="tabs-content" class="flex-1 outline-none safari-tab-content w-full mt-0 focus:outline-none"></div><div data-state="inactive" data-orientation="horizontal" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="radix-_R_jausnj9flb_-trigger-color-experimentation" hidden="" id="radix-_R_jausnj9flb_-content-color-experimentation" tabindex="0" data-slot="tabs-content" class="flex-1 outline-none safari-tab-content w-full mt-0 focus:outline-none"></div></div></div></div></section><section class="w-full py-16 bg-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6"><div class="space-y-24 max-w-6xl mx-auto"><div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center"><div class="w-full md:w-1/2 relative"><div class="relative h-64 md:h-80 w-full overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-lg bg-green-50 flex items-center justify-center"><div class="p-4 w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center"><img src="/imgs/stats-highlight/hairstyle_ai_compare.png" alt="Trained on Over 500+ Professional Hairstyles" class="max-w-full max-h-full object-contain"/></div><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/10 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div></div></div><div class="w-full md:w-1/2"><h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Trained on Over 500+ Professional Hairstyles</h2><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">Our hairstyle AI is powered by an extensive database of professional hairstyles from top salons worldwide. This comprehensive training ensures that every hairstyle try on looks natural and suits different face shapes, hair types, and personal styles — helping you find the perfect look with confidence.</p></div></div><div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse gap-8 items-center"><div class="w-full md:w-1/2 relative"><div class="relative h-64 md:h-80 w-full overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-lg bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center"><div class="p-4 w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center"><img src="/imgs/stats-highlight/hairstyle_ai_boy.jpg" alt="Lightning-Fast Results in Under 10 Seconds" class="max-w-full max-h-full object-contain"/></div><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/10 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div></div></div><div class="w-full md:w-1/2"><h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Lightning-Fast Results in Under 10 Seconds</h2><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">Our AI hairstyle changer delivers stunning transformations in seconds. Upload your photo and instantly see yourself with any hairstyle — from classic cuts to trendy styles, complete with realistic hair textures and colors that match your features perfectly.</p><ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700"><li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-500 mt-1">✓</span><span><strong>Instant hairstyle transformation</strong> with realistic results</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-500 mt-1">✓</span><span><strong>Face shape analysis</strong> for perfect hairstyle matching</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-500 mt-1">✓</span><span><strong>High-quality output</strong> ready for download and sharing</span></li></ul></div></div><div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center"><div class="w-full md:w-1/2 relative"><div class="relative h-64 md:h-80 w-full overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-lg bg-indigo-50 flex items-center justify-center"><div class="p-4 w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center"><img src="/imgs/stats-highlight/hairstyle_ai_woman.jpg" alt="Supports All Hair Types and Styles" class="max-w-full max-h-full object-contain"/></div><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/10 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div></div></div><div class="w-full md:w-1/2"><h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Supports All Hair Types and Styles</h2><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">Whether you want a short pixie cut, long layered hair, or bold color changes, our hairstyle AI works with all hair types and styles. Perfect for men and women of all ages, our AI hairstyle changer adapts to your unique features and preferences.</p><div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 mt-4"><div class="bg-indigo-50 p-3 rounded-lg text-center"><p class="text-sm font-medium text-indigo-800">Short Styles</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-600">Pixie, Bob, Crew Cut</p></div><div class="bg-indigo-50 p-3 rounded-lg text-center"><p class="text-sm font-medium text-indigo-800">Long Styles</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-600">Layers, Waves, Straight</p></div><div class="bg-indigo-50 p-3 rounded-lg text-center"><p class="text-sm font-medium text-indigo-800">Color Options</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-600">Natural, Fashion, Highlights</p></div><div class="bg-indigo-50 p-3 rounded-lg text-center"><p class="text-sm font-medium text-indigo-800">Trendy Cuts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-600">Modern, Classic, Edgy</p></div></div></div></div><div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse gap-8 items-center"><div class="w-full md:w-1/2 relative"><div class="relative h-64 md:h-80 w-full overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-lg bg-purple-50 flex items-center justify-center"><div class="p-4 w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center"><img src="/imgs/stats-highlight/hairstyle_ai_security.png" alt="Privacy and Security First" class="max-w-full max-h-full object-contain"/></div><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/10 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div></div></div><div class="w-full md:w-1/2"><h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Privacy and Security First</h2><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">All photos uploaded to our hairstyle AI are securely encrypted and processed in real-time. No images are stored, shared, or used for any training purposes. Your hairstyle try on sessions remain completely private and secure — your data is yours alone.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class="w-full py-12 md:py-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50 dark:from-gray-950 dark:to-gray-900"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6"><div class="text-center mb-12"><h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 mb-4">Hair Decisions Are Hard — Hairstyle AI Makes Them Easy</h2><p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">We understand the struggle of choosing the perfect hairstyle. Here&#x27;s how our AI hairstyle changer solves your biggest hair dilemmas with confidence.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto"><div data-slot="card" class="text-card-foreground gap-6 py-6 border-0 shadow-xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl h-full flex flex-col"><div data-slot="card-header" class="@container/card-header grid auto-rows-min grid-rows-[auto_auto] items-start gap-1.5 has-data-[slot=card-action]:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] [.border-b]:pb-6 pb-2 pt-6 px-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-50 to-gray-100 dark:from-gray-800 dark:to-gray-900 border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 text-center"><div data-slot="card-title" class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white flex items-center justify-center gap-2"><span class="bg-red-100 dark:bg-red-900/30 p-2 rounded-full"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="h-6 w-6 text-red-500 dark:text-red-400" height="1em" width="1em" x