></svg></div><div><h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-green-600 dark:group-hover:text-green-500 transition-colors">Risk-Free Virtual Hairstyle Try On</h3><p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">See exactly how any hairstyle will look on you before committing to a cut with our realistic hairstyle AI preview technology.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 hover:bg-green-50/50 dark:hover:bg-green-950/20 transition-colors group"><div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-green-100/60 dark:bg-green-900/30 p-3 rounded-full"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="h-6 w-6 text-green-600 dark:text-green-500" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M12 22C6.47715 22 2 17.5228 2 12C2 6.47715 6.47715 2 12 2C17.5228 2 22 6.47715 22 12C22 17.5228 17.5228 22 12 22ZM11.0026 16L18.0737 8.92893L16.6595 7.51472L11.0026 13.1716L8.17421 10.3431L6.75999 11.7574L11.0026 16Z"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-green-600 dark:group-hover:text-green-500 transition-colors">Instant Hairstyle Preview Technology</h3><p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">Try hundreds of different styles, lengths, and colors instantly with our AI hairstyle changer without any risk or commitment.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 hover:bg-green-50/50 dark:hover:bg-green-950/20 transition-colors group"><div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-green-100/60 dark:bg-green-900/30 p-3 rounded-full"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="h-6 w-6 text-green-600 dark:text-green-500" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M12 22C6.47715 22 2 17.5228 2 12C2 6.47715 6.47715 2 12 2C17.5228 2 22 6.47715 22 12C22 17.5228 17.5228 22 12 22ZM11.0026 16L18.0737 8.92893L16.6595 7.51472L11.0026 13.1716L8.17421 10.3431L6.75999 11.7574L11.0026 16Z"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-green-600 dark:group-hover:text-green-500 transition-colors">Instant Hair Color Experimentation</h3><p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">Experiment with different looks using our easy-to-use interface that lets you upload your photo and try various styles within minutes.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 hover:bg-green-50/50 dark:hover:bg-green-950/20 transition-colors group"><div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-green-100/60 dark:bg-green-900/30 p-3 rounded-full"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="h-6 w-6 text-green-600 dark:text-green-500" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M12 22C6.47715 22 2 17.5228 2 12C2 6.47715 6.47715 2 12 2C17.5228 2 22 6.47715 22 12C22 17.5228 17.5228 22 12 22ZM11.0026 16L18.0737 8.92893L16.6595 7.51472L11.0026 13.1716L8.17421 10.3431L6.75999 11.7574L11.0026 16Z"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-green-600 dark:group-hover:text-green-500 transition-colors">Free AI Hairstyle Changer Preview</h3><p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">Save time and money by avoiding salon consultations and hair disasters - know exactly what you want before you go to the stylist.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="p-6 mt-auto"><button class="w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white py-3 px-6 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors shadow-md hover:shadow-lg">Try Hairstyle AI Now<svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="h-5 w-5" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M16.1716 10.9999L10.8076 5.63589L12.2218 4.22168L20 11.9999L12.2218 19.778L10.8076 18.3638L16.1716 12.9999H4V10.9999H16.1716Z"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-50/50 to-blue-50/20 dark:from-gray-950 dark:to-gray-900 relative overflow-hidden"><div class="absolute inset-0"><div class="absolute top-32 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-50/60 dark:bg-blue-900/15 rounded-full filter blur-3xl"></div><div class="absolute bottom-32 right-1/4 w-80 h-80 bg-indigo-50/60 dark:bg-indigo-900/15 rounded-full filter blur-3xl"></div></div><div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10"><div class="text-center mb-16"><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4 tracking-tight">How to Use Our Hairstyle AI</h2><p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-light">Transform your look in minutes with our easy-to-use AI hairstyle changer. Follow these simple steps to discover your perfect hairstyle.</p></div><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8"><div data-slot="card" class="text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl py-6 group relative overflow-hidden border-0 bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-md shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:-translate-y-1 h-[28rem]"><div data-slot="card-content" class="p-8 flex flex-col h-full"><div class="flex-shrink-0 mb-6"><div class="relative"><div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 to-blue-500 rounded-2xl shadow-lg shadow-blue-400/25 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:shadow-xl group-hover:shadow-blue-400/40 transition-all duration-300"><span class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">1</span></div><div class="absolute inset-0 w-12 h-12 bg-blue-300/30 rounded-2xl scale-0 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-500 -z-10"></div></div></div><div class="flex-1 flex flex-col"><div class="space-y-5"><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white leading-tight group-hover:text-blue-500 dark:group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors duration-300">Upload Your Photo</h3><div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed"><p>Start by uploading a clear, front-facing photo of yourself. Our hairstyle AI works best with good lighting and a neutral background. Make sure your current hairstyle and face shape are clearly visible for the most accurate results.</p></div></div></div><div class="absolute bottom-0 left-6 right-6 h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-blue-200/60 dark:via-blue-700/40 to-transparent group-hover:via-blue-300/80 dark:group-hover:via-blue-400/60 transition-colors duration-300"></div></div></div><div data-slot="card" class="text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl py-6 group relative overflow-hidden border-0 bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-md shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:-translate-y-1 h-[28rem]"><div data-slot="card-content" class="p-8 flex flex-col h-full"><div class="flex-shrink-0 mb-6"><div class="relative"><div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 to-blue-500 rounded-2xl shadow-lg shadow-blue-400/25 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:shadow-xl group-hover:shadow-blue-400/40 transition-all duration-300"><span class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">2</span></div><div class="absolute inset-0 w-12 h-12 bg-blue-300/30 rounded-2xl scale-0 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-500 -z-10"></div></div></div><div class="flex-1 flex flex-col"><div class="space-y-5"><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white leading-tight group-hover:text-blue-500 dark:group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors duration-300">Browse and Select Hairstyles</h3><div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed"><p>Explore our extensive library of hairstyles organized by categories like short, medium, long, and trending styles. Our AI hairstyle changer offers options for all hair types, making it easy to find styles that interest you.</p></div></div></div><div class="absolute bottom-0 left-6 right-6 h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-blue-200/60 dark:via-blue-700/40 to-transparent group-hover:via-blue-300/80 dark:group-hover:via-blue-400/60 transition-colors duration-300"></div></div></div><div data-slot="card" class="text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl py-6 group relative overflow-hidden border-0 bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-md shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:-translate-y-1 h-[28rem]"><div data-slot="card-content" class="p-8 flex flex-col h-full"><div class="flex-shrink-0 mb-6"><div class="relative"><div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 to-blue-500 rounded-2xl shadow-lg shadow-blue-400/25 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:shadow-xl group-hover:shadow-blue-400/40 transition-all duration-300"><span class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">3</span></div><div class="absolute inset-0 w-12 h-12 bg-blue-300/30 rounded-2xl scale-0 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-500 -z-10"></div></div></div><div class="flex-1 flex flex-col"><div class="space-y-5"><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white leading-tight group-hover:text-blue-500 dark:group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors duration-300">Watch the AI Magic Happen</h3><div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed"><p>Our advanced hairstyle AI processes your photo and seamlessly applies your chosen hairstyle. The process takes just seconds, and you&#x27;ll see a realistic preview of how you&#x27;ll look with your new hairstyle try on.</p></div></div></div><div class="absolute bottom-0 left-6 right-6 h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-blue-200/60 dark:via-blue-700/40 to-transparent group-hover:via-blue-300/80 dark:group-hover:via-blue-400/60 transition-colors duration-300"></div></div></div><div data-slot="card" class="text-c