v class="absolute inset-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-purple-400/20 dark:bg-purple-500/20 scale-0 group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform duration-500 -z-10"></div></div><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white group-hover:text-purple-600 dark:group-hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors duration-300">Lisa K.</h4><p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 truncate">Busy Mom</p></div></div><div class="absolute bottom-0 left-8 right-8 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-purple-200/60 dark:via-purple-700/40 to-transparent group-hover:via-purple-300/80 dark:group-hover:via-purple-600/60 transition-colors duration-300"></div></div></div><div data-slot="card" class="text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 py-6 group overflow-hidden border-0 bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-800/80 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-3xl shadow-lg shadow-purple-500/10 dark:shadow-black/20 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-purple-500/20 dark:hover:shadow-black/40 transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02] relative h-full"><div data-slot="card-content" class="p-8 flex flex-col h-full"><div class="flex items-center gap-1 mb-6"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 group-hover:text-yellow-500 transition-colors duration-300" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M12.0006 18.26L4.94715 22.2082L6.52248 14.2799L0.587891 8.7918L8.61493 7.84006L12.0006 0.5L15.3862 7.84006L23.4132 8.7918L17.4787 14.2799L19.054 22.2082L12.0006 18.26Z"></path></svg><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 group-hover:text-yellow-500 transition-colors duration-300" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M12.0006 18.26L4.94715 22.2082L6.52248 14.2799L0.587891 8.7918L8.61493 7.84006L12.0006 0.5L15.3862 7.84006L23.4132 8.7918L17.4787 14.2799L19.054 22.2082L12.0006 18.26Z"></path></svg><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 group-hover:text-yellow-500 transition-colors duration-300" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M12.0006 18.26L4.94715 22.2082L6.52248 14.2799L0.587891 8.7918L8.61493 7.84006L12.0006 0.5L15.3862 7.84006L23.4132 8.7918L17.4787 14.2799L19.054 22.2082L12.0006 18.26Z"></path></svg><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 group-hover:text-yellow-500 transition-colors duration-300" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M12.0006 18.26L4.94715 22.2082L6.52248 14.2799L0.587891 8.7918L8.61493 7.84006L12.0006 0.5L15.3862 7.84006L23.4132 8.7918L17.4787 14.2799L19.054 22.2082L12.0006 18.26Z"></path></svg><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 group-hover:text-yellow-500 transition-colors duration-300" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M12.0006 18.26L4.94715 22.2082L6.52248 14.2799L0.587891 8.7918L8.61493 7.84006L12.0006 0.5L15.3862 7.84006L23.4132 8.7918L17.4787 14.2799L19.054 22.2082L12.0006 18.26Z"></path></svg></div><blockquote class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 flex-grow relative"><span class="text-4xl text-purple-200 dark:text-purple-800 absolute -top-2 -left-2 font-serif">&quot;</span><span class="relative z-10">I wanted a hairstyle that would work well for my active lifestyle. The hairstyle AI helped me explore different sporty cuts and find one that looks great whether I&#x27;m at the gym or out with friends. Super convenient tool!</span><span class="text-4xl text-purple-200 dark:text-purple-800 absolute -bottom-4 -right-2 font-serif">&quot;</span></blockquote><div class="flex items-center gap-4 mt-auto"><div class="relative"><span data-slot="avatar" class="relative flex size-8 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-full w-12 h-12 border-2 border-purple-100 dark:border-purple-900/50 shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-xl group-hover:shadow-purple-500/20 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:-translate-y-0.5"></span><div class="absolute inset-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-purple-400/20 dark:bg-purple-500/20 scale-0 group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform duration-500 -z-10"></div></div><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white group-hover:text-purple-600 dark:group-hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors duration-300">Carlos D.</h4><p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 truncate">Fitness Trainer</p></div></div><div class="absolute bottom-0 left-8 right-8 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-purple-200/60 dark:via-purple-700/40 to-transparent group-hover:via-purple-300/80 dark:group-hover:via-purple-600/60 transition-colors duration-300"></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="faq" class="py-16"><div class="container"><div class="text-center"><h2 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-semibold">Frequently Asked Questions About Hairstyle AI</h2><p class="mt-6 font-medium text-muted-foreground">Got questions? We&#x27;ve got answers! Contact us at support@hairstyleai.ai</p></div><div class="mx-auto mt-14 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-12"><div class="flex gap-4"><span class="flex size-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-sm border border-primary font-mono text-xs text-primary">1</span><div><div class="mb-2 flex items-center justify-between"><h3 class="font-semibold">How accurate is the hairstyle AI?</h3></div><p class="text-md text-muted-foreground">Our AI hairstyle changer uses advanced machine learning algorithms trained on millions of hairstyle images. While results are highly realistic, remember that the final outcome may vary slightly based on your hair texture, thickness, and styling preferences. We recommend showing the AI result to your stylist as a reference.</p></div></div><div class="flex gap-4"><span class="flex size-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-sm border border-primary font-mono text-xs text-primary">2</span><div><div class="mb-2 flex items-center justify-between"><h3 class="font-semibold">What types of photos work best with the hairstyle AI?</h3></div><p class="text-md text-muted-foreground">For the best hairstyle try on results, use a clear, front-facing photo with good lighting. Avoid sunglasses, hats, or anything covering your hairline. The AI works best when it can clearly see your face shape and current hair.</p></div></div><div class="flex gap-4"><span class="flex size-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-sm border border-primary font-mono text-xs text-primary">3</span><div><div class="mb-2 flex items-center justify-between"><h3 class="font-semibold">Is my photo data safe with your hairstyle AI?</h3></div><p class="text-md text-muted-foreground">Absolutely! We take privacy seriously. Your photos are processed securely and deleted from our servers after 24 hours. We never store, share, or use your images for any purpose other than generating your hairstyle transformations.</p></div></div><div class="flex gap-4"><span class="flex size-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-sm border border-primary font-mono text-xs text-primary">4</span><div><div class="mb-2 flex items-center justify-between"><h3 class="font-semibold">Can I try multiple hairstyles with one photo?</h3></div><p class="text-md text-muted-foreground">Yes! Once you upload a photo, you can try as many different hairstyles as you want. Our AI hairstyle changer lets you experiment with various cuts, lengths, and colors using the same base image.</p></div></div><div class="flex gap-4"><span class="flex size-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-sm border border-primary font-mono text-xs text-primary">5</span><div><div class="mb-2 flex items-center justify-between"><h3 class="font-semibold">Do you offer hairstyles for both men and women?</h3></div><p class="text-md text-muted-foreground">Definitely! Our hairstyle AI includes hundreds of styles for both men and women. From classic cuts to trendy styles, short pixies to long layers, masculine fades to feminine curls - we have something for everyone.</p></div></div><div class="flex gap-4"><span class="flex size-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-sm border border-primary font-mono text-xs text-primary">6</span><div><div class="mb-2 flex items-center justify-between"><h3 class="font-semibold">How much does it cost to use the hairstyle AI?</h3></div><p class="text-md text-muted-foreground">We offer free credits to new users so you can try our AI hairstyle changer without any cost. After that, you can purchase additional credits at affordable rates. Check our pricing page for current offers and packages.</p></div></div><div class="flex gap-4"><span class="flex size-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-sm border border-primary font-mono text-xs text-primary">7</span><div><div class="mb-2 flex items-center justify-between"><h3 class="font-semibold">Can I use the hairstyle AI on my mobile phone?</h3></div><p class="text-md text-muted-foreground">Yes! Our hairstyle try on feature works perfectly on smartphones, tablets, and computers. The mobile experience is optimized for easy photo uploads and smooth hairstyle browsing.</p></div></div><div class="flex gap-4"><span class="flex size-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-sm border border-primary font-mono text-xs text-primary">8</span><div><div class="mb-2 flex items-center justify-between"><h3 class="font-semibold">What if I don&#x27;t like the hairstyle AI results?</h3></div><p class="text-md text-muted-foreground">No problem! You can try different styles until you find one you love. Our AI hairstyle changer offers hundreds of options, so you&#x27;re sure to find something that suits your taste and preferences.</p></div></div></div></div></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main><section id="footer" class="py-16"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8"><footer><div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-between gap-10 text-center lg:flex-row lg:text-left"><div class="flex w-full max-w-96 shrink flex-col items-center justify-between gap-6 lg:items-start"><div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 lg:justify-start"><img src="/logo.png" alt="Hairstyle AI - Your AI Hairstyle Changer" class="h-11"/><p class="text-3xl font-semibold">Hairstyle AI</p></div><p class="mt-6 text-md text-muted-foreground">Hairstyle AI is your ultimate AI hairstyle changer that helps you discover the perfect look before you visit the salon. Try on hundreds of hairstyles instantly with our advanced artificial intelligence technology. Whether you&#x27;re looking for a dramatic change or just want to experiment with different hair colors, our hairstyle try on feature makes it easy and fun.</p></div><ul class="flex items-center space-x-6 text-muted-foreground"><li class="font-medium hover:text-primary"><a href="https://www.instagram.com/hairstyleailab" target="_blank"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="size-4 cursor-pointer" style="cursor:default" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M12.001 9C10.3436 9 9.00098 10.3431 9.00098 12C9.00098 13.6573 10.3441 15 12.001 15C13.6583 15 15.001 13.6569 15.001 12C15.001 10.3427 13.6579 9 12.001 9ZM12.001 7C14.7614 7 17.001 9.2371 17.001 12C17.001 14.7605 14.7639 17 12.001 17C9.24051 17 7.00098 14.7629 7.00098 12C7.00098 9.23953 9.23808 7 12.001 7ZM18.501 6.74915C18.501 7.43926 17.9402 7.99917 17.251 7.99917C16.5609 7.99917 16.001 7.4384 16.001 6.74915C16.001 6.0599 16.5617 5.5 17.251 5.5C17.9393 5.49913 18.501 6.0599 18.501 6.74915ZM12.001 4C9.5265 4 9.12318 4.00655 7.97227 4.0578C7.18815 4.09461 6.66253 4.20007 6.17416 4.38967C5.74016 4.55799 5.42709 4.75898 5.09352 5.09255C4.75867 5.4274 4.55804 5.73963 4.3904 6.17383